title: Leave A Legacy Of Faith | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Leave A Legacy Of Faith | Joel Osteen
description:
The decisions we make should make things easier for those that will come after us. We can store up blessings and favor for our future generations by living a life of excellence and integrity. 


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
